---Description---
 NDC to RGB shader
 Color of every vertex in every object should be set using a shader such
 that the coordinates of the vertex in Normalized Device Coordinates (-1 to +1
 in x,y,z) determines the color of the vertex. 

 DONE IN ONE LINE IN vertex file and frag file.

